{% comment %}
  ============================================================================
  Custom Footer Block Section
  ============================================================================
  
  DESCRIPTION:
  A comprehensive custom footer section for Shopify themes with advanced 
  multi-language support and JobRad partnership integration. This component 
  provides flexible footer blocks with customizable call-to-action buttons, 
  localized content, and geo-targeted partner banners for enhanced user 
  engagement and conversion optimization.
  
  CORE FEATURES:
  • Multi-Language Support: Full localization for English, German, French, Finnish
  • JobRad Partnership Integration: Conditional geo-targeting for Germany/Austria
  • Flexible Footer Blocks: Up to 3 customizable blocks with unique styling
  • Responsive Design: Mobile-optimized layouts with adaptive grid system
  • Background Image Support: Custom or default fallback images for each block
  • Customizable Button System: Individual colors, text, and URL configuration
  • Hover Effects: Smooth CSS transitions and interactive elements
  • Grid Layout Adaptation: Smart mobile layout for optimal user experience
  • Country-Based Filtering: Conditional content display based on user location
  • Accessibility Features: ARIA labels and semantic HTML structure
  
  BLOCK CONFIGURATION:
  • Background Images: Custom image picker with default fallbacks
  • Button Text: Localized text for all supported languages (EN/DE/FR/FI)
  • Button URLs: Custom link destinations for each block
  • Button Colors: Customizable background colors with hover effects
  • Responsive Behavior: Automatic adaptation for mobile devices
  
  JOBRAD INTEGRATION:
  • Conditional Display: Based on country detection (Germany/Austria only)
  • Localized Partner Text: Multi-language support for partnership messaging
  • Custom JobRad Icon: Dedicated icon rendering with hover animations
  • Configurable JobRad URL: Customizable link to JobRad partnership pages
  • Geo-Targeting Logic: Uses Shopify's localization.country.iso_code
  
  RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:
  • Desktop Layout: Horizontal layout with equal-width blocks (flex: 1)
  • Mobile Layout: Adaptive grid system for optimal mobile experience
  • 3-Block Mobile Grid: First block full width, remaining blocks split 50/50
  • Flexible Button Sizing: CSS clamp() for optimal readability across devices
  • Height Adaptation: Variable heights (500px desktop, 400px mobile)
  
  DEFAULT PRESETS:
  1. "Need help choosing?" - Contact form block with orange button (#f2a112)
  2. "Book a test ride" - Test ride booking block with blue button (#2b7dde)
  3. "Find a dealer" - Dealer locator block with red button (#fa6959)
  
  TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:
  • CSS Custom Properties: Maintainable styling with CSS variables
  • Conditional Liquid Rendering: Locale-based content switching
  • Country-Based Content Filtering: Geo-targeted feature display
  • Optimized Image Loading: Shopify's img_url filter with size optimization
  • Semantic HTML Structure: Proper accessibility and SEO optimization
  • Smooth Animations: CSS transitions for enhanced user experience
  
  DEPENDENCIES AND RELATED FILES:
  
  Snippet Dependencies:
  • snippets\icon-jobrad.liquid - JobRad logo SVG rendering with custom styling
  
  Related Snippet Files:
  • snippets\leasing-partner.liquid - Partner integration (jobrad,bikeleasing,deutsche,businessbike)
  
  Theme Structure Files:
  • layout\theme.liquid - Main theme layout with global configurations
  • sections\footer.liquid - Standard footer section (separate from custom footer)
  
  SCHEMA CONFIGURATION:
  • Section Name: "Custom footer block"
  • Category: "Custom"
  • Max Blocks: 3 footer blocks maximum
  • Settings: JobRad banner toggle, JobRad URL, multi-language partner text
  • Block Settings: Background image picker, multi-language button text, button URL, button color
  • Default Preset: Complete 3-block setup with localized content
  
  STYLING FEATURES:
  • CSS Custom Properties: --banner-height (500px), --mobile-banner-height (400px), --jobrad-icon-width (120px)
  • Responsive Grid System: Flexible layout adaptation for mobile devices
  • Hover Animations: Transform effects and box-shadow enhancements
  • Color Customization: Individual button color configuration
  • Typography: Clamp-based font sizing for optimal readability
  • Overlay Effects: Semi-transparent overlays for better text readability
  
  BROWSER SUPPORT:
  • Modern browsers with CSS Grid and Flexbox support
  • CSS Custom Properties (CSS Variables) compatibility
  • CSS clamp() function for responsive typography
  • Transform and transition animations
  • Shopify Liquid templating engine
  
  PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
  • Optimized image loading with Shopify's img_url filter
  • Conditional rendering to reduce unnecessary DOM elements
  • CSS-only animations for smooth performance
  • Minimal JavaScript dependencies (none required)
  • Efficient Liquid logic for locale detection
  
  ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
  • Semantic HTML structure with proper heading hierarchy
  • ARIA labels for interactive elements
  • Keyboard navigation support
  • Screen reader compatibility
  • High contrast button designs
  • Focus indicators for interactive elements
  
  LOCALIZATION SUPPORT:
  • English (EN): Default language with fallback support
  • German (DE): Full localization for German market
  • French (FR): Complete French language support
  • Finnish (FI): Finnish market localization
  • Automatic locale detection via request.locale.iso_code
  • Country-based feature toggling via localization.country.iso_code
  
  USAGE EXAMPLES:
  • E-commerce footer with call-to-action blocks
  • Partnership banner integration (JobRad)
  • Multi-language website footer sections
  • Conversion-optimized footer layouts
  • Mobile-first responsive footer designs
  
  ============================================================================
{% endcomment %}

